1 var PacketReader = require('../../PacketReader'),
  2   PacketWriter = require('../../PacketWriter'),
  3   LOBReadPacket = require('../../LOBReadPacket'),
  4   CAS = require('../../../constants/CASConstants');
  5 
  6 exports['test_LOBReadPacket'] = function (test) {
  7   test.expect(116);
  8   var packetReader = new PacketReader();
  9   var packetWriter = new PacketWriter();
 10 
 11   var packedLobHandle = new Buffer([0, 0, 0, 33, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 79, 102, 105, 108, 101, 58,
 12                                     67, 58, 92, 67, 85, 66, 82, 73, 68, 92, 100, 97, 116, 97, 98, 97, 115, 101, 115, 92, 100, 101, 109, 111, 100,
 13                                     98, 47, 108, 111, 98, 47, 99, 101, 115, 95, 48, 56, 50, 47, 116, 101, 115, 116, 95, 108, 111, 98, 46, 48, 48,
 14                                     48, 48, 49, 51, 54, 49, 57, 55, 54, 53, 52, 50, 48, 48, 48, 48, 48, 48, 95, 56, 49, 52, 53, 0
 15   ]);
 16   var lobHandle =
 17   {
 18     lobType         : CAS.CUBRIDDataType.CCI_U_TYPE_BLOB, //BLOB type
 19     packedLobHandle : packedLobHandle,
 20     fileLocator     : 'file:C:\\CUBRID\\databases\\demodb/lob/ces_670/test_lob.00001361976357078000_1538',
 21     lobLength       : 4
 22   };
 23   var options = {
 24     casInfo      : [0, 255, 255, 255],
 25     lobObject    : lobHandle,
 26     position     : 0,
 27     lengthToRead : 4,
 28     dbVersion    : '8.4.1'
 29   };
 30   var lobReadPacket = new LOBReadPacket(options);
 31   lobReadPacket.write(packetWriter);
 32   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[3], 120); //total length
 33 
 34   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[4], 0); //casInfo
 35   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[5], 255); //casInfo
 36   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[6], 255); //casInfo
 37   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[7], 255); //casInfo
 38 
 39   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[8], CAS.CASFunctionCode.CAS_FC_LOB_READ);
 40   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[12], 95);
 41   for (var i = 0; i < packedLobHandle.length; i++) {
 42     test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer().slice(13, 110)[i], packedLobHandle[i]);
 43   }
 44   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[111], 8);
 45   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[119], 0);
 46   test.equal(packetWriter._toBuffer()[127], 4);
 47 
 48   packetReader.write(new Buffer([0, 0, 0, 15,
 49                                  0, 255, 255, 255,
 50                                  0, 0, 0, 4,
 51                                  1, 2, 3, 4]));
 52   lobReadPacket.parse(packetReader);
 53 
 54   test.equal(lobReadPacket.casInfo[0], 0); //casInfo
 55   test.equal(lobReadPacket.casInfo[1], 255); //casInfo
 56   test.equal(lobReadPacket.casInfo[2], 255); //casInfo
 57   test.equal(lobReadPacket.casInfo[3], 255); //casInfo
 58 
 59   test.equal(lobReadPacket.responseCode, 4);
 60 
 61   test.equal(lobReadPacket.errorCode, 0);
 62   test.equal(lobReadPacket.errorMsg, '');
 63 
 64   test.equal(lobReadPacket.lobBuffer[0], 1);
 65   test.equal(lobReadPacket.lobBuffer[1], 2);
 66   test.equal(lobReadPacket.lobBuffer[2], 3);
 67   test.equal(lobReadPacket.lobBuffer[3], 4);
 68   test.done();
 69 };
